commit.message:
Coerce to string where pass object into string interpolation (#1494)

String interpolation, it will convert object to string using #to_s automatically.
Unexpected objects are accepted because all object have #to_s.

```
irb(main):001> "hello #{Object.new}"
=> "hello #<Object:0x000000011dd30770>"
```

commit.message:
Fix ImageList#sort! that should return self (#1481)

Standard Ruby implementation of ! method returns self.
However, ImageList#sort! has wrong behaviour.

```
imgl = Magick::ImageList.new
p imgl.object_id       # => 60
p imgl.sort!.object_id # => 80
```

This patch follows that behaviour.
